data.value:
Cruise Control.Net is an Automated Continuos Integration server, implemented using the Microsoft .Net Framework.
CCTray is a system tray application that enables you to see 'at a glance' the state of your projects from any machine on your network.
Unit4 modifications: - New menu option added: Overview of CI machines - New menu option added: Hide succeeded tasks - New menu option added: Hide building tasks
